title: Annoying Timers
text: I love this game and Ive been playing it since I was a kid. The only reason I am leaving a review, however, is that I’m frustrated with the timed games, where you have 1 minute and you college timers to add 10 seconds. It’s frustrating because sometimes the timers spawn in places that i literally cannot get to without super sneakers. I assume that this is an intentional choice, but it makes the game less appealing for me if it comes down to luck and not skill.
